---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="House Painters Moonah | Rental, Strata & Commercial"
  description="House painters in Moonah — inner-north homes, rental repaints, strata exteriors and shopfront/commercial work. Cold-climate prep, low-VOC paints, low-disruption scheduling. Free quote."
  canonical="https://hobarthousepainters.com.au/moonah/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Moonah &middot; Derwent Park &middot; West Moonah &middot; Lutana</span>
      <h1>House painters in <span class="accent">Moonah</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Moonah is the Hobart&rsquo;s busy inner-north &mdash; a mix of older
        residential homes, rentals, unit blocks and a thriving commercial strip.
        We do the lot: interior and exterior house repaints, strata and
        body-corporate exteriors, and shopfront work scheduled around trading.
        Proper prep, fixed quotes, minimal fuss.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Moonah</span>
      <h2>Painting Moonah properties.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Mixed residential &mdash; houses, units and rentals.</h3>
        <p>
          Moonah, Derwent Park and Lutana are a real mix &mdash; older houses,
          post-war stock, unit blocks and a high proportion of rental and
          investment property. For landlords and agents, a clean, durable repaint
          lifts rentability and protects exposed timber from the damp climate.
          We turn rentals around fast on a fixed quote, using hard-wearing
          low-VOC interior paints so the place is ready for the next tenant
          quickly. See <a href="/services/interior-painting/">interior house
          painting</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Strata and body-corporate exteriors.</h3>
        <p>
          The inner-north has plenty of unit and townhouse complexes. Their
          rendered and weatherboard common-property exteriors take a beating in
          Hobart&rsquo;s damp weather &mdash; mould on shaded walls, chalking
          render, flaking trim. We work with committees and managing agents,
          provide a clear itemised scope, coordinate access across units, and
          prep properly so the maintenance cycle is a long one. See
          <a href="/services/commercial-painting/">commercial &amp; strata
          painting</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Shopfronts and the Main Road strip.</h3>
        <p>
          Moonah&rsquo;s commercial strip means shopfronts, offices and
          hospitality fitouts that can&rsquo;t afford to shut for a paint job. We
          schedule around trading &mdash; early mornings, evenings, weekends or
          staged areas &mdash; manage public access safely around the work, and
          use low-VOC paints so a freshly painted space is back in use quickly.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Older homes &mdash; lead-safe where needed.</h3>
        <p>
          Pre-1970 Moonah homes may carry lead paint under later coats. Where
          that&rsquo;s the case we prepare lead-safe to AS 4361.2 &mdash; no
          dry sanding that spreads lead dust, proper containment and clean-up.
          See <a href="/services/heritage-painting/">heritage &amp; weatherboard
          painting</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Moonah jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Quick-turnaround interior repaint between tenants</li>
          <li>Strata block exterior repaint coordinated with the body corporate</li>
          <li>Shopfront and office repaint scheduled around trading hours</li>
          <li>Exterior repaint of an older home, lead-safe prep where required</li>
          <li>Roof clean and recoat on a unit block or family home</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/sandy-bay/">Sandy Bay</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/glenorchy/">Glenorchy</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/kingston/">Kingston</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/new-town/">New Town</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/hobart-region/">All Greater Hobart</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Moonah painting quote.</h2>
        <p>Houses, rentals, strata and shopfronts. Proper prep, fixed price, scheduled around you.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
